    <ul>
      <li><WikiLink slug="pages/dark_matter_halos" text="Dark matter halos" /> — halo mass definitions and clustering-based inference</li>
      <li><WikiLink slug="pages/black_hole_mass" text="Black hole mass" /> — BH mass measurements and scaling relations</li>
      <li><WikiLink slug="pages/eddington_ratio" text="Eddington ratio" /> — accretion rate diagnostics</li>
      <li><a href="/concepts/galaxy-bimodality">Galaxy bimodality</a> — environmental role vs. internal processes in quenching and BH growth</li>
